On a database Oracle, it's impossible to convert the column Search_Field from varchar to clob.

We must use this script before updating JIRA :
{code:sql}
ALTER TABLE AUDIT_LOG ADD (tmp  CLOB);

UPDATE AUDIT_LOG SET tmp = SEARCH_FIELD;
COMMIT;

ALTER TABLE AUDIT_LOG DROP COLUMN SEARCH_FIELD;

ALTER TABLE AUDIT_LOG RENAME COLUMN tmp TO SEARCH_FIELD;
{code}

